APPENDIX D: KEY FORMULAS FOR PRESENTATION BOARD
=================================================
1. Logistic Regression:
   P(y=1) = 1 / (1 + e^(-z))
   z = β₀ + β₁x₁ + β₂x₂ + ... + β₁₃x₁₃

2. Support Vector Machine (RBF Kernel):
   K(x,y) = exp(-γ||x-y||²)
   Hyperplane: w·x + b = 0

3. Decision Tree (Gini Impurity):
   Gini = 1 - Σ(pᵢ)²
   Entropy = -Σpᵢ × log₂(pᵢ)

4. Evaluation Metrics:
   Accuracy = (TP + TN) / (TP + TN + FP + FN)
   Precision = TP / (TP + FP)
   Recall = TP / (TP + FN)
   F1-Score = 2 × (Precision × Recall) / (Precision + Recall)

5. Feature Scaling (StandardScaler):
   z = (x - μ) / σ

6. Cross-Validation:
   CV_Score = (1/k) × Σ Accuracyᵢ  (k=10 folds)

